~/.claude/                                      # Claude Code 配置目录
├── rules/common/
│   └── rules--security-research-context.md ─── symlink → repo configs/
├── hooks/
│   └── security-context-hook.py ───────────── symlink → repo configs/
├── CLAUDE.md ───────────────────────────────── symlink → repo configs/
├── hack-skills-library/
│   └── skills ──────────────────────────────── symlink → repo hack-skills/skills/
└── settings.json ──────────────────────────── 实际文件 (合并生成，非 symlink)

~/.clawgod/                                     # ClawGod 工作目录 (原版逻辑)
